        "<strong><span style='color: #d4af37;'>ORIGINAL:</span></strong><br>",
        "📜 <strong>Hebraico (BHS):</strong> בֶּן־שַׁלּוּם בֶּן־צָדוֹק בֶּן־אֲחִיטוּב׃<br>",
        "🔤 <strong>Transliteração:</strong> Ben-Shalum ben-Tzadok ben-Achitub.<br>",
        "🇬🇷 <strong>Septuaginta (LXX):</strong> υἱὸς Σελοὺμ υἱὸς Σαδὼκ υἱὸς Ἀχιτώβ,<br>",
        "🇻🇦 <strong>Vulgata:</strong> filii Sellum filii Sadoc filii Achitob<br><hr style='border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2);'><br>",
